#subtitle: Outside of electoral politics, the SPD runs a social world onto itself.

= Party Organizations

In addition to being a political party, the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> is a social world onto itself, with a vast array of associated organizations which serve the social needs of their members from cradle to grave.

- @newspapers: Fund more newspapers and journalists.
- @welfare: Fund more mutual aid and welfare programs.
- @culture: Fund sports leagues, educational, and cultural programs.
- @rb: Fund and increase recruiting to the Reichsbanner, our self-defense organization.
- @youth: We have the reputation of being a party for old men. Support the youth organizations.
- @nothing: Do not increase funding for any program.
- @easy_discard

@newspapers
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources
on-arrival: resources -= 1; media_timer -= 6;
go-to: media

@welfare
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources
on-arrival: resources -= 1; workers_aid += 1; unemployed_spd += (4+workers_aid)*(1 - dissent); workers_spd += (2*workers_aid)*(1-dissent) if Q.juchacz_advisor; workers_spd += 2*(1-dissent) if black_thursday_seen

We have increased funding to Workers' Welfare. [? if black_thursday_seen > 0 : In an age of economic crisis, this will be helpful for improving our standing among the unemployed. ?]

@culture
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources
on-arrival: resources -= 1; cultural_organizations += 1; left_dissent -= 5; left_dissent -= cultural_organizations if sa_force < 25; center_dissent -= 5; center_dissent -= cultural_organizations if sa_force < 25; labor_dissent -= 5; labor_dissent -= cultural_organizations if sa_force < 25; reformist_dissent -= 5; reformist_dissent-= cultural_organizations if sa_force < 25; neorevisionist_dissent -= 5; neorevisionist_dissent -= cultural_organizations if sa_force < 25

It is not enough for the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> to solely be a political party. The Worker Singer's League, Worker's Sports, and our schools and libraries are crucial to our members' lives. Funding these organizations makes our members more committed to the party, even when our policies might not be to their liking.

[? if sa_force >= 25 : However, it feels frivolous to spend on sports and choirs when the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">fascists</span> are murdering us in the streets. ?]

