@youth
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources
view-if: not rb_explode
on-arrival: resources -= 1; rb_strength += 50; rb_militancy += 0.02; young_socialists += 1; left_strength += 5; neorevisionist_strength += 5; workers_spd += 2*(1-dissent) if Q.seydewitz_advisor; new_middle_spd += 2*socialism if Q.seydewitz_advisor; radicalization += 1;

Our new youth members flock to the left or neorevisionist wings of the party, and also bring new radicalism to the Reichsbanner.

@nothing

We do not fund any party organizations.

- @return: Continue...
